caption.body: Fans of quarterback Peyton Manning, playing in his 18th season and leading the Denver Broncos this weekend in the AFC title game, can view his Colts jersey from his rookie season if they are traveling through SFO’s Terminal 3 during our exhibition on the history of the NFL, The Nation’s Game.
